        <Parent_String>intaglio printing processes [300199636], printing processes [300199635], printing and printing processes and techniques [300185289], image-making processes and techniques [300053159], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
